reviewText: My favorite Disney characters are always getting into hot water.  Fun to follow....

This set is an excellent collection of Chip 'n Dale.  Some of the cartoons here are very difficult to find.  IT IS REGION 2, AND REQUIRES A REGION 2 PLAYER OR A MULTIREGION PLAYER.  Those 1 star reviews from people who bought it and did not READ the disk region info should be ignored.
Contents of the disk are:
1.  Working for Peanuts
2. Out On A Limb
3.  Corn Chips
4. Toy Tinkers
5. Three for Breakfast
6. Donald Applecore
7. Dragon Around
8. Winter Storage
Will not work in DVD player.
Didn't work. Kept cause it would cost more than I paid to send it back
wrong place region 2. Had to down load from U tube for free.
Well, I guess I should have paid more attention but it is made for British DVD and not compatible with U.S. machines. $10  lesson learned!
This won't work in a US DVD player.  My loss.

Ok maybe just cute family fun - always good for the soul, enjoy this with those young or just young at heart
